{
  "video_id": "sqlBe8CdPuc",
  "title": "Using ocean currents for cleanup",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 934.0,
      "end_time": 2334.0,
      "text": "BOYAN SLAT: My name is Boyan Slat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2334.0,
      "end_time": 4671.0,
      "text": "and I'm the founder and CEO at the Ocean Cleanup, where we've"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4671.0,
      "end_time": 6572.0,
      "text": "developed the world's first technology to rid"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6572.0,
      "end_time": 8908.0,
      "text": "the world's oceans of plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8908.0,
      "end_time": 11377.0,
      "text": "Right now, millions of tons of plastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11377.0,
      "end_time": 12645.0,
      "text": "have entered the oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12645.0,
      "end_time": 15414.0,
      "text": "And they concentrate in these five massive areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15414.0,
      "end_time": 17316.0,
      "text": "called ocean garbage patches."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17316.0,
      "end_time": 19652.0,
      "text": "The largest one is between Hawaii and California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19652.0,
      "end_time": 21754.0,
      "text": "called the Great Pacific Garbage Patch."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21754.0,
      "end_time": 25758.0,
      "text": "In the past, people proposed to clean it up with boats and nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25758.0,
      "end_time": 27861.0,
      "text": "to sort of go fishing for plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27861.0,
      "end_time": 30130.0,
      "text": "But this would take many tens of thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30130.0,
      "end_time": 32832.0,
      "text": "it would cost many billions of dollars to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32832.0,
      "end_time": 34100.0,
      "text": "And one day, I realized that the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 35601.0,
      "text": "currents, actually they rotate."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 35601.0,
      "end_time": 38037.0,
      "text": "The plastic doesn't stay in one spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 38037.0,
      "end_time": 40106.0,
      "text": "So I thought, well, maybe instead"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 40106.0,
      "end_time": 42141.0,
      "text": "of going after the plastic, why don't we"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42141.0,
      "end_time": 43742.0,
      "text": "let the plastic come to us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 43742.0,
      "end_time": 45577.0,
      "text": "Why don't we use the natural ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 45577.0,
      "end_time": 47546.0,
      "text": "currents in our advantage?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 47546.0,
      "end_time": 50015.0,
      "text": "Then we came up with this passive system that"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 50015.0,
      "end_time": 51851.0,
      "text": "is comprised out of these very long"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 51851.0,
      "end_time": 55921.0,
      "text": "floating barriers, which then allows the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 55921.0,
      "end_time": 57656.0,
      "text": "to basically clean itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 57656.0,
      "end_time": 59692.0,
      "text": "So we just stay there, the current"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 59692.0,
      "end_time": 61527.0,
      "text": "brings the plastic towards us."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 61527.0,
      "end_time": 63262.0,
      "text": "And that way we can first concentrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 63262.0,
      "end_time": 65798.0,
      "text": "the plastic before we take it out and ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 65798.0,
      "end_time": 67900.0,
      "text": "it to land for recycling."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 67900.0,
      "end_time": 72105.0,
      "text": "And we then calculated that with one such system deployed for 10"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 72105.0,
      "end_time": 74240.0,
      "text": "years, we can clean up about half"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 74240.0,
      "end_time": 85485.0,
      "text": "the Great Pacific Garbage Patch."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 85485.0,
      "end_time": 88420.0,
      "text": "It's very hard to deny that this is a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 88420.0,
      "end_time": 92391.0,
      "text": "You can just literally go to a beach or take out a boat"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92391.0,
      "end_time": 94093.0,
      "text": "and see it with your own eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94093.0,
      "end_time": 96195.0,
      "text": "It's so visible."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96195.0,
      "end_time": 100433.0,
      "text": "Really no one can deny that this is something that we"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 100433.0,
      "end_time": 103069.0,
      "text": "need to do something about."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103069.0,
      "end_time": 106172.0,
      "text": "I never really thought of myself as an entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106172.0,
      "end_time": 109975.0,
      "text": "I just enjoyed making things."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 109975.0,
      "end_time": 112945.0,
      "text": "It's really just about the feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112945.0,
      "end_time": 114948.0,
      "text": "that you get when you have an idea in your mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114948.0,
      "end_time": 116915.0,
      "text": "and then seeing that become reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 116915.0,
      "end_time": 121654.0,
      "text": "I think there's really no better feeling in the world than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 121654.0,
      "end_time": 124356.0,
      "text": "I've been sort of this inventor all my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124356.0,
      "end_time": 129395.0,
      "text": "but I didn't really have a real problem to work on."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129395.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132064.0,
      "text": "And that changed when I was 16 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132064.0,
      "end_time": 133432.0,
      "text": "and I was diving in Greece."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133432.0,
      "end_time": 136636.0,
      "text": "And I realized, I came across more plastic bags than fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136636.0,
      "end_time": 140073.0,
      "text": "And I thought, well, why can't we just keep this up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140073.0,
      "end_time": 142942.0,
      "text": "And I think that was the one question"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142942.0,
      "end_time": 145744.0,
      "text": "that kickstarted it all."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145744.0,
      "end_time": 147046.0,
      "text": "I would describe myself as someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147046.0,
      "end_time": 150716.0,
      "text": "who is quite obsessive when I have an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150716.0,
      "end_time": 154921.0,
      "text": "and I just continue thinking about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 154921.0,
      "end_time": 157357.0,
      "text": "I think it took about a year just playing around"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157357.0,
      "end_time": 159592.0,
      "text": "with different concepts in my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159592.0,
      "end_time": 162661.0,
      "text": "until I had something that I thought could work."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162661.0,
      "end_time": 166399.0,
      "text": "And then of course, it went out of my head and onto paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 166399.0,
      "end_time": 168700.0,
      "text": "And then to get started, of course I"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168700.0,
      "end_time": 170570.0,
      "text": "think that was just the hardest part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170570.0,
      "end_time": 174207.0,
      "text": "finding the resources to be able to actually get going."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174207.0,
      "end_time": 176408.0,
      "text": "But thankfully it went viral on the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176408.0,
      "end_time": 177944.0,
      "text": "was being shared millions of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 177944.0,
      "end_time": 181214.0,
      "text": "which then allowed me to build the initial team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181214.0,
      "end_time": 183750.0,
      "text": "as well as raise the initial capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 183750.0,
      "end_time": 186352.0,
      "text": "through crowdfunding to actually start and make this dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 186352.0,
      "end_time": 190055.0,
      "text": "a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190055.0,
      "end_time": 193025.0,
      "text": "I'm 100% sure that we can do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193025.0,
      "end_time": 195094.0,
      "text": "If I would have thought that success wasn't"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195094.0,
      "end_time": 197462.0,
      "text": "one of the possible outcomes, I probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197462.0,
      "end_time": 198864.0,
      "text": "wouldn't have started it."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198864.0,
      "end_time": 201767.0,
      "text": "I'm sure it's challenging, and I'm sure we'll encounter a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201767.0,
      "end_time": 204770.0,
      "text": "more surprises and problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204770.0,
      "end_time": 206872.0,
      "text": "But that's how innovation works."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 206872.0,
      "end_time": 211477.0,
      "text": "It's just a continuous list of problems to be solved."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 211477.0,
      "end_time": 213078.0,
      "text": "And eventually you will hopefully"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 213078.0,
      "end_time": 223078.0,
      "text": "solve that one last problem and then you've succeeded."
    }
  ]
}